results.title: Kiya Foods
results.description: On an unknown date, data allegedly belonging to Kiya Foods, a now defunct India-based online food store, was leaked online. The data contains names, email addresses, usernames, passwords, IPs and additional personal information. This leak is being publicly shared on a messaging platform.
results.site_description: Kiya Foods is a now defunct online food store headquartered in Kerala, India.
